snippet.title: The Crooked Man EN PV
snippet.description:
There was a crooked man, and he walked a crooked mile...
This is the first title in the series known as The Strange Man, developed by Uri Games.
Experience the myriad horrors awaiting David as he moves into his new house.
PLAYISM: http://playism-games.com/game/331/the-crooked-man
Steam: http://store.steampowered.com/app/736570/The_Crooked_Man/
